---
// Fundations
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<sectio>
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-12">
    <Text
      tag="h2"
      variant="displayMD"
      class="text-base-900 text-balance font-display"
    >
      A Message from Our CEO
    </Text>
    <div
      class="relative group bg-base-50 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12 items-start"
    >
      <div class="relative w-full aspect-square">
        <iframe
          src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1141054297?fl=ip&fe=ec"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full"
          frameborder="0"
          allow="autoplay; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
        ></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-2 p-4 lg:p-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
          <Text
            tag="p"
            variant="textLG"
            class="text-base-900 font-medium leading-relaxed"
          >
Since its founding in 2018, Madavi Agency has evolved from a brand-focused marketing firm into Madavi Inc, a company dedicated to building the backend infrastructure necessary for sustainable growth. CEO leadership emphasizes that while creative campaigns capture attention, true business success requires intelligent, adaptive systems rather than just AI hype. By shifting the focus from polished content to robust AI-driven systems, the firm now provides the structural foundation that allows businesses to automate execution and free up teams for high-level human innovation.          <div>
            <Text tag="p" variant="textLG" class="text-base-900 font-display">
              Kune Ambuyo
            </Text>
            <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600 mt-1">
              CEO & Founder, Madavi Inc
            </Text>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Wrapper>
</sectio>
